Miscellaneous Sources for HisoftBasic (V2), MaxonBasic 3  (revised 03.Jan.98)
You need the iff.library, © by Christian A. Weber for a Part of this.
The iff.library is available from Aminet: util/libs/iff.library-23.lha.

Contents:

    bh/blib/ILBMSupport.bas            Include for easy using iff.library
    bh/blib/ImageSupport.bas           Include for creating imagestructures
    
    bh/iff.bc                          Constants for iff.library
    bh/iff.bh                          Headerfile for iff.library
    
    bmap/IFF.bmap                      Library-BMAP

    examples/Images/ImageDemo#?        Demos for using IntuiImages
    examples/Pictures/IFF-Lib_Demo#?   Demo for using the iff.library
    examples/Pictures/ViewDTPic#?      Demos for using the datatypes.library
    examples/Bilder/#?                 Testpictures in many formats

    tools/ILBM2BAS                     Converter ILBM -> IntuiImage


